lines.text: Take a quick survey & enter for the chance
to WIN a $250 Sprouts gift card. Go to:
Bring this back anytime from September 16-22*
Qualifying purchase calculated after applying all
other coupons and discounts and excludes
amounts for tax, alcohol, postage & gift cards.
Maximum discount $10. Not valid online or on
prior purchases. To use in store scan receipt
barcode. Limit one per transaction. Cannot be
cornbined with other Sprouts cash-off offers or
employee discount. No cash redemption unless
required by law @ 1/100¢. Void if duplicated,
sold or transferred. Subject to all applicable laws.
Not valid in our Tucson or Nashville stores.
